                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.00/826: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Carter</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-06-09T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 9, 1930—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>58. National City Bank requests full text of Liberian Department of State
                    Communication Number 286 D of June 4. Please cable for possible
                    transmission.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
